# Filament — the lead: electric and SUSTAINING. The pluck-everything
# habit was wrong for this idiom: the reference stabs sing while held.
# Pulse core through the resonant ladder, a bite on the attack from the
# filter ping, then the note OPENS INTO a held tone (sustain 0.55) and
# releases naturally. Drive 2.8 for wire and current. No LFO.
waveform 1
pulse_width 0.22
osc2_wave 2
osc2_pitch 0
osc2_level 0.15
osc3_wave 0
osc3_pitch 0
osc3_level 0
detune 2
sub 0.15
circuit 1
key_track 0.8
osc_fm 0
sync 0
ring 0
glide 0
attack 0.006
decay 0.6
sustain 0.55
release 0.35
filter_env 1.2
filter_attack 0.001
filter_decay 0.3
filter_sustain 0.5
filter_release 0.3
cutoff 1200
resonance 1.1
drive 2.8
saturation 1.15
hpf 80
volume 0.5
octave 4
noise 0
fuzz 0
spring 0.12
lfo_rate 0.5
lfo_shape 0.5
lfo_pitch 0
lfo_filter 0
lfo_pwm 0
